  <brief_title>Preoperative Education With Illustrations Enhances Effect of Tetracaine Mucilage in Alleviating Postoperative CRBD</brief_title>
  <official_title>Preoperative Education With Cartoon Illustrations Enhances the Effect of Tetracaine Mucilage in Alleviating Postoperative Catheter-related Bladder Discomfort: a Prospective, Randomized, Controlled Study</official_title>
